SubjectYukon Court of Justice - Deputy Judges

AttachmentsAttachment
subject: Yukon Court of Justice - Deputy Judges
precis:
Order 1) to appoint the following judges to be Deputy Judges of the Supreme Court of Yukon to hold office during good behaviour until attaining the age of seventy-five years:
(a) the Honourable Francis W. Cole
(b) the Honourable Elizabeth A. Hughes
(c) the Honourable James W. Williams
(d) the Honourable Stephen D. Hillier
(e) the Honourable J. Keith Bracken
(f) the Honourable Miriam A. Maisonville
(g) the Honourable John Z. Vertes

2) to fix the remuneration of the Honourable Jonh Z. Vertes, former judge of the supreme Court of the Northwest Territories
